    ];

    const morals = [
      "ğŸŒŸ Imagination is the key to unlocking endless possibilities.",
      "ğŸ’– True friendship can conquer even the greatest challenges.",
      "ğŸŒˆ Embrace the unknown, for it holds the greatest treasures.",
      "ğŸš€ Courage isn't the absence of fear, but the triumph over it.",
